HMG/Courtland Properties Inc.


            
            HMG/Courtland Properties, Inc. engages in the ownership and management of income-producing commercial properties. Its other investments consist primarily of nominal equity interests in various privately-held entities, including limited partnerships. The company's investments in marketable securities include equity and debt securities issued primarily by large capital companies or government agencies with readily determinable fair values in varying industries. HMG/Courtland Properties was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Coconut Grove, FL.

            
