HMG/Courtland Properties Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















hmg/courtland properties inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
HMG/Courtland Properties, Inc. is a corporation which qualifies as a real estate investment trust. The Company invests individually or through joint ventures in income-producing commercial properties. HMG owns properties in Texas, Florida, and the Northeastern United States.




